quotelist.aquote: The more I like myself, the more others will like me.
I am becoming better with each day.
I will ask for help if I need it.
I am proud to represent the values that matter to me and my community.
Character is strength,I will do the right things when no one is looking.

My character is a sum total of my habits, My habits are formed by my repeated decisions and every decision I make will either build up my character or bring me down and eventually break me down, So I will choose to make my right informed decisons. (Derek Prince).
